             was indicted for <rs id="t18320906-75-off439" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320906-75-off439" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320906-75-off439" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320906-75-cd440" type="crimeDate">16th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-75-off439 t18320906-75-cd440"></join>, 1 hat, value 4s.; 2 pair of unmade boots, value 5s., and 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-75-victim722" type="victimName">
                           Daniel 
                           Mason
                        <interp inst="t18320906-75-victim722" type="surname" value="Mason"></interp>
